{"type":null,"faqId":36928,"title":"荣耀小K手表摘下和带上是否有提醒？如何识别的？摘下会强行报警吗？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\r\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span>\"1.手表摘下时，APP侧会提示消息：宝贝摘下了手表。<br>\n2.手表带上没有提醒。<br>\n3.摘表提醒时，手机侧不会有响铃，也不会强行报警。<br>\n<br>\n注：<br>\n手表背面的光传感器可以测量手臂与手表的距离，手表通过光传感器的测量距离判断手表是否摘下或佩戴。<br>\n请保持光传感器洁净、不要被异物阻挡。\" <br>\n</span></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2028","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440638664000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":32,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"K1-G01,荣耀小K,儿童手表,K1,摘表提醒,戴手表,摘手表,摘下手表,脱下手表,带上手表,佩戴,感应器,光传感器,提醒,提示,强行报警,APP状态","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}